                <h1 class="text-markdown-h1">Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="bold">Last Updated Jan. 16, 2019</p>
                <p>
                    The team at Brainiark, Inc. (“Brainiark,” “Company,” “we,” “us,” “our”) knows that you care about how your information
                    is collected, used and shared, and we take your privacy seriously. Please read this Privacy Policy carefully to learn
                    more about our privacy practices.
                </p>
                <h2 class="text-markdown-h2" >What Does This Privacy Policy Cover?</h2>
                <p>
                    This Privacy Policy applies to <a href="https://brainiark.com/" target="_blank">https://brainiark.com/</a>. This Privacy Policy does not apply to websites, applications or
                    other services that provide their own separate privacy statements or policies. Our Website may contain links to other
