                    details, please contact us at <a href="mailto:kingdavidsbusiness@gmail.com">kingdavidsbusiness@gmail.com</a>.
                </p>

                <hr>

                <h2 class="text-markdown-h2">for users of our website from the european union</h3>
                <h3 class="text-markdown-h3">your rights regarding your personal information</h3>
